---
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Privacy Policy | Bernardo Souza</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Privacy policy for the Bernardo Souza website."
    />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#2563eb" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="legal-page">
      <section class="legal-container">
        <a href="/en/" class="legal-back">← Back to website</a>

        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p>
          This website collects personal data voluntarily provided through the
          contact form, such as name, email, company, role and description of
          the request.
        </p>

        <h2>Purpose</h2>
        <p>
          The data is used only to respond to contact requests, assess potential
          collaboration opportunities and prepare service proposals related to
          Power Platform, Business Intelligence, automation and integrations.
        </p>

        <h2>Data sharing</h2>
        <p>
          The data is not sold or shared with third parties for external
          marketing purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>Tools used</h2>
        <p>
          The form may be processed through an external form tool. Responses are
          used exclusively for contact management and commercial follow-up.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          To request correction or deletion of your data, send an email to:
          <a href="mailto:bernardosantiagodesouza@gmail.com">
            bernardosantiagodesouza@gmail.com
          </a>
        </p>

        <p class="legal-note">Last updated: 2026.</p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
